clause.head:
connect(This :: wxEvtHandler(),
EventType :: wxEventType(),
Options :: [Option]) ->
ok

subtype.string:
Option =
{id, integer()} |
{lastId, integer()} |
{skip, boolean()} |
callback |
{callback, function()} |
{userData, term()}
